-- Obtain first FCI_BUYER with FCBU_BUYER_DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH

SQL_STMT_U.val: select FCBU_MEMBER_NO_EF, FCBU_MEMBER_NO_IF from :1/FCBU, :1/FCSE where :2 and FCSE_SELLER_ADMNO = :3 and FCSE_SELLER_CLNTNO = :4 and FCSE_MEMBER_NO_EF = FCBU_MEMBER_NO_EF and FCSE_MEMBER_NO_IF = FCBU_MEMBER_NO_IF and Upper(FCSE_SELLER_NO) = Upper(FCBU_SELLER_NO) for fetch only
